All Classes

Class Summary 
Class Description
AuditorPage
Extends JPanel to create a GUI menu for a profile with auditor privileges to navigate to the Profile, Landing, Media, or CreateBallot page.
CreateBallot
Extends JPanel to create a GUI menu for a profile with auditor privileges to create a ballot with an arbitrary number of candidates running for a position.
Database
Implements the functionality for connecting to mySQL database and executing queries.
Driver  
Frame
Extends JFrame to create a JFrame containing all JPanel pages of the voting system.
GUIComponents
Implements functionality for dark mode, language selection, profile updating, and constructing voting ballots.
Home
Extends JPanel to create a GUI menu for navigating to Profile, Vote, and Landing pages includes language selection, dark mode, voting progress bar, and blocking vote access if user has already voted.
LandingPage
Extends JPanel to create a GUI page for logging into the system or navigating to Registration page.
MediaPage
Extends JPanel to create a GUI page for displaying results of elections for different positions.
Profile
Extends JPanel to create a GUI page for displaying user profile information Includes dark mode, language selection, and a back button.
Registration
Extends JPanel to create a GUI page for registering a new profile.
VotePage
Extends JPanel to create a GUI page for voting for a candidate.
VoteTab
Extends JPanel to create a tab displaying a ballot of candidates running for one position.
